00:15:25.940 --> 00:15:26.780
Oo.

00:15:49.520 --> 00:15:50.420
Kamahalan,

00:15:50.500 --> 00:15:52.490
Humiling si Xu Wanning ng madla
kasama ang Prinsesa.

00:16:19.740 --> 00:16:20.980
Kahanga-hanga!

00:16:25.020 --> 00:16:26.710
Ako, si Xu Wanning, ay nagbibigay galang sa iyo.

00:16:27.250 --> 00:16:30.300
Narinig ko na lang ang tunog ng sitar,

00:16:30.300 --> 00:16:31.400
matunog at makapangyarihan.

00:16:31.560 --> 00:16:32.660
Ilang maikling tala,

00:16:32.660 --> 00:16:34.500
